    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Airtight or nearly airtight, box-like containers, of metal, wood, or plastic; used for storing bread and other baked goods to keep them fresh.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
